         SidebarMenu.uxml â€” Collapsible Hamburger Sidebar
        ============================================
         A standalone sidebar that slides in/out.
         Demonstrates: transitions, class toggling,
         dynamic element creation, search, category tabs.

         CONCEPTS SHOWN:
         1. Transition animations via USS (slide, fade, scale)
         2. Class toggling for state changes (open/closed)
         3. Dynamic child creation in C#
         4. Pseudo-class styling (:hover, :active, :checked)
         5. ScrollView for long lists
         6. TextField for live search
         7. Foldout for collapsible sections
    -->

